	(text_box "DRV8245 (VQFN-HR) IPROPI current sense calculation\nAIPROPI = 202 uA/A → I_IPROPI = I_load * 202uA/A\nFor full-scale motor current = 28 A:\nI_IPROPI,max = 28 * 202uA = 5.656 mA\nChoose R_IPROPI = 680 Ω → V_ADC = I_IPROPI * R_IPROPI\nV_ADC at 28 A ≈ 3.85 V (slightly above 3.3 V, adjust resistor if strict limit required)\nV_ADC at 14 A ≈ 1.9 V\nUse 1% metal-film resistor + optional 10-100 nF capacitor for noise filtering"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 200.66 68.58 0)
		(size 73.66 22.86)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
